          <h2>
            About Us
          </h2>
          <div class="box clearfix">
            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></i>
            <p>
              At long last, we’re finally engaged! Thirteen years after we first met backstage at the Grand Ole Opry, Johnny proposed during a live performance at the London Ice House in London, Ontario. In the past thirteen years, we spent a lot of time together performing and touring along with the rest of the Carter family. We’ve written and performed a number of songs together, including "It Ain't Me Babe," "Jackson" and "If I Were a Carpenter." I guess all those times performing together really solidified our bond. Our pasts have led us to each other and we cannot wait to begin this next journey in life side by side.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <h2>
            Our Story
          </h2>
          <div class="box clearfix">
            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></i>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3>Hers</h3>
              <p>
                Johnny is my best friend. He is charming, reliable, funny, and sensitive all in one big, attractive man. He may have his quirks, but that’s what I love most about him.
              </p>
              <p>
                Johnny and I’s friendship was the perfect starting point for our growing love for each other. As friends, we learned about each other, enjoyed each other’s company, and began to fall in love. Looking back, I can’t imagine it starting any other way. 
              </p>
              <p>
                In life you interact with a lot of different people, but only once in a lifetime do you find someone who is your perfect match. Johnny is perfect for me. He's everything I've always dreamed of and I'm so excited to spend the rest of my life with him!
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3>His</h3>
              <p>
                June is amazing. When I first met her I knew she was amazing and every passing day remin ds me of just how amazing she is! What really blows me away is her incredibly unique blend of talents, interests, and personality. She's a talented artist, always excited about trying new things, and a genuinely loving person. June can be doing anything from singing onstage to hanging out at home and she has the same happy, welcoming demeanor that makes her a joy to be around.
              </p>
              <p>
                It has been an amazing journey with June so far and I am looking forward to starting a new life together. June means so much to me and I can’t believe she is actually going to marry me.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
